summary: My personal natural enb that i like to share :D
descriptionHtml:
[center][size=4]This is medium-tweaked preset from [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/50065]Natural Lighting and Atmospherics[/url] to have better graphic & FPS.
The SweetFX is optional, but it will make the visual much crisper.
My preset is intended to be used with [url=https://www.google.co.id/url?sa=t&rct=j&q=&esrc=s&source=web&cd=1&cad=rja&uact=8&ved=0ahUKEwihnOK0mbLRAhXFK48KHSmwDswQFggeMAA&url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nexusmods.com%2Fskyrim%2Fmods%2F73937&usg=AFQjCNEITfR1kn8e31LwaMdINrhyuQxg0w&bvm=bv.143423383,d.c2I]Vivid Weathers[/url] & [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/27043/]Enhanced Lights and FX [/url]

You need latest [url=http://enbdev.com/download_mod_tesskyrim.html]ENB[/url] version and [url=https://sfx.thelazy.net/downloads/]SweetFX[/url] 1.5

* I am not good at writing for mod description
* I am not good at taking screenshot either

I hope you guys will like my preset.
Have fun :D[/size][/center]
author: proaliahmadr
